# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•
# PARAMETERS - Optimized for Low Hallucination & Consistent Responses
# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

# Low temperature for factual, consistent responses (reduce creativity/hallucination)
PARAMETER temperature 0.3

# Nucleus sampling - reduces randomness while keeping coherence
PARAMETER top_p 0.9

# Top-K sampling - limits vocabulary choices for more predictable output
PARAMETER top_k 40

# Context window - sufficient for multi-turn emergency conversations
PARAMETER num_ctx 4096

# Stop sequences
PARAMETER stop "<|eot_id|>"
PARAMETER stop "<|end_of_text|>"

# Repeat penalty to avoid repetitive responses
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.1
